---
import Layout from '@/components/Layout.astro';
import WaitlistForm from '@/components/WaitlistForm.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Root & Ritual" description="Root & Ritual is a natural scalp care brand creating clean, lightweight, practical routines for modern women with oily or greasy-prone scalps.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-16">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-moss">About</p>
    <h1 class="mt-4 font-serif text-5xl">Simple scalp care for modern routines.</h1>
    <div class="prose-brand mt-8">
      <p>Root & Ritual was created around a simple idea: scalp care should be as thoughtful as skincare, but lighter, cleaner, and easier to use in real life.</p>
      <p>Many modern women deal with roots that feel oily quickly, hair that looks flat by the next day, or routines that rely too heavily on dry shampoo. Our focus is natural scalp care that feels practical rather than precious.</p>
      <p>The brand direction is clean, lightweight, and daily. We are building toward formulas that support a fresh-feeling scalp routine without heavy textures, harsh positioning, or medical promises.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-10">
      <WaitlistForm />
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
